      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor surface scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal use, but no significant dents or structural damage. The paint is intact with no rust. The interior is clean with moderate wear on the upholstery and no major damage. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well and has been maintained regularly.",
